title: India pencil in top men, women cricketers for Asian Games
description: India is sending its top men's and women's cricket teams to the Asian Games in Japan, aiming for Olympic qualification in 2028. Suryakumar Yadav and Harmanpreet Kaur will captain the T20 squads. This move signifies cricket's growing importance in multi-sport events, with the BCCI prioritizing established players due to a clear international calendar.
